  • Facial Recognition Security System
    Development of Real-Time Face Recognition for Smart Door Lock Security System
    • Enhancing Security and Convenience through Facial Recognition
    Call To Action
    01
    1. PAPER TITLE : Face Recognition Based Smart Attendance System
    ABSTRACT:
    A computer-based student attendance checking system is required that supports the faculty to keep records of attendance. We have used an intelligent attendance system based on face recognition in this project. We have proposed to implement a "Smart Attendance System for Face Recognition" through this large applications are incorporated.
    • Implementing Haar Cascade for face detection and LBPH Face Recognizer for face recognition in smart door locks.
    02
    Advantages
    • A Face Recognition Based Smart Attendance System improves accuracy, efficiency, security, and convenience while offering scalability and integration capabilities, making it a robust solution for modern attendance management needs.
    03
    Author
    •  A Arjun Raj
    04
    Publication Date
    • 2020

    06

  • Facial Recognition Security System
    Development of Real-Time Face Recognition for Smart Door Lock Security System
    • Enhancing Security and Convenience through Facial Recognition
    Call To Action
    01
    2. PAPER TITLE : Development of Real-Time Face Recognition for Smart Door Lock Security System using Haar Cascade and OpenCV LBPH Face Recognizer
    ABSTRACT: Face recognition is a technology that is widely used in security systems. In a door security system, facial recognition can be used to open the door simply by recognizing the face of the door owner. This study aims to develop a real-time facial recognition system for smart locking doors using Haar Cascade and OpenCV LBPH Face Recognizer
    • Implementing Haar Cascade for face detection and LBPH Face Recognizer for face recognition in smart door locks.
    02
    Advantages
    • The use of Haar Cascade for face detection and LBPH Face Recognizer for face recognition in a smart door lock security system offers a robust solution that combines accuracy, real-time processing, security enhancement, user convenience, and scalability, making it suitable for modern security applications.
    03
    Author
    • Daniel Anando Wangean
    04
    Publication Date
    • 2023
